gory:Football in Cambodia| ]]\n\n\n{{Cambodia-sport-stub}}\n{{footy-stub}}\n", "name_user": "John of Reading", "label": "safe", "comment": "Typo/generalfixes, replaced: teams best performance \u2192 team's best performance", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Football_in_Cambodia"}
{"title_page": "Sarath Mandava", "text_new": "{{Infobox person\n| name        =Sarath Mandava\n| image       = \n| birth_name  = Sarath Babu Mandava\n| birth_place = [[Ongole]], [[Andhra Pradesh]], [[India]]\n| occupation  = director <br /> writer <br /> executive producer <br /> cinematographer <br />\n| years_active= 2009 \u2013 present\n| alma mater = [[ITM University, Raipur|ITM University]], [[Southern New Hampshire University]]\n}}\n'''Sarath Mandava''' is an [[Indian ]] screenwriter, director, cinematographer and executive producer known for his works in [[Tamil cinema]], and [[Telugu cinema]].<ref name=\"cinestaan.com\">{{cite web|url=https://www.cinestaan.com/people/sarath-mandava-95557/filmography |title=Sarath Mandava Movies and Filmography |work=cinestaan.com |accessdate=2020-04-10 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\"Film News\">{{cite news|url=https://m.timesofindia.com/entertainment/tamil/movie-details/ko-2/movieshow/61292650.cms|title=Ko 2 Movie: Showtimes, Review, Songs, Trailer, Poster, News..|work=Times of India|page=1|accessdate=10 April 2020}}</ref> \nSarath made his directorial debut with a political thriller Tamil version film ''[[Ko 2]]''. In 2012, he has written/ co-written Ajith Kumar's ''[[Billa II]]'' as screenplay and story writer.<ref>{{cite web |title=Billa 2 Review - Tamil Movie Billa 2 Review |url=https://www.nowrunning.com/movie/8726/tamil/billa-2/3794/review.htm |website=NOWRUNNING |accessdate=14 December 2018 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Review : (2012) |url=http://www.sify.com/movies/billa-2-review-tamil-15002888.html |website=www.sify.com |accessdate=14 December 2018}}</ref>. He has written dialogues for the telugu version of the same film released on 13 Jul 2012 with title [[David Billa]]. <ref name=\"CNN News\">{{cite news|url=https://www.news18.com/news/india/audio-release-of-telugu-film-david-billa-480966.html|title=Audio Release of Telugu Film David Billa|work=News 18|page=1|accessdate=10 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nSarath Mandava started his career in Films after quitting his Software Career. He went to Film School in London promoted by Rain Dance and did a Script Writing course in Straight Curve Film School, Kent, UK. He started working as Associate Director and Co-writer in various films before directing his first debut  [[Tamil film]] ''[[Ko 2]]''. He worked as Executive Producer for [[Telugu film]] ''[[Potugadu]]''.  \n\n==Filmography==\n\n===As director===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\" border=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\"\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#cccccf\"\n! Year !! Film !! Actors !! Language !! Notes\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Ko 2]]'' || rowspan=\"2\" |[[Bobby Simha]], [[Prakash Raj], [[Nikki Galrani]] || [[Tamil language|Tamil]] ||\n|}\n\n===As writer ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\" border=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\"\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#cccccf\"\n! Year !! Film !! Role !! Language !! Notes\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Kamoshi]]'' || Dialogue Writer || [[Hindi language|hindi]] ||\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Ko 2]]'' || Additional Story and Screenplay || Tamil ||\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[Billa II|Billa 2 ]]'' || Story, Screenplay || Tamil||\n|-\n| 2012 || ''[[David Billa]]'' ||  Telugu Version Dialogues || Telugu ||\n|-\n|}\n\n\n===As cinematographer===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\" border=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\"\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#cccccf\"\n! Year !! Film !! Actors !! Language !! Notes\n|-\n| 2016 || ''[[Tulasi Dalam (film) |Tulasi Dalam]]'' || rowspan=\"2\" |[[RP Patnaik | RP Patnaik ]] || [[Telugu language|Telugu]] ||\n| 2010 || ''[[Broker (film)|Broker]]'' || rowspan=\"2\" | [[Srihari (actor)|Srihari ]], [[RP Patnaik | RP Patnaik]] || [[Telugu language|Telugu]] ||\n\n|}\n\n===As executive producer===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\" border=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\"\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#cccccf\"\n! Year !! Film !! Actors !! Language !! Notes\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[https://www.imdb.com/title/tt10300254/ Evadu Thakkuva Kadu]'' || rowspan=\"2\" |[https://www.imdb.com/name/nm8500000/?ref_=tt_ov_st_sm Vikram Sahidev] || [[Telugu language|Telugu]] ||\n| 2013 || ''[[Potugadu]]'' || rowspan=\"2\" |[[Manchu Manoj|Rocking Star Manoj]] || [[Telugu language|Telugu]] ||\n\n|}\n\n\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://www.indiaglitz.com/billa-2-ko-2-sarath-mandava-emotional-speech-about-death-of-lyricist-namuthukumar--news-165247 Young scriptwriter of Ajith film, emotional talk about Na.Muthukumar]\n* [https://www.123telugu.com/mnews/press-note-sarath-mandava-to-direct-sequel-for-rangam.html Sequel of Tamil Film Ko (telugu Rangam) to be directed Debut - Sarath Mandava]\n* [https://www.onlykollywood.com/sarath-mandava-interview-ajith-sir-is-like-a-big-brother-i-learnt-a-lot-about-life-from-him/ Sarath Mandava Interview]\n* [https://www.thehindu.com/features/cinema/debutant-director-sarath-speaks-about-his-film-ko2/article8600475.ece Hindu About Debutant Director Sarath Mandava]\n* [https://www.moviebuff.com/ko-2 Interesting elements of Ko 2 ]\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mandava, Sarath}}\n[[:Category:Tamil film directors]]\n[[:Category:Telugu film directors]]\n[[:Category:Tamil Film Writers]]\n[[:Category:Telugu Film Writers]]\n[[:Category:Indian Film Writers]]\n[[:Category:20th-century births]]\n[[:Category:Living people]]\n[[:Category:Telugu male actors]]\n[[:Category:American male actors of Indian descent]]\n[[:Category:Film directors f