s (Maltese footballer)|Michael Woods]]\n|{{flagicon|MLT}}\n|align=left|2010\n|align=left|2012\n|-\n|align=left|[[Joe Brincat]]\n|{{flagicon|MLT}}\n|align=left|March 20, 2012\n|align=left|2012\n|-\n|align=left|[[Mark Wright (footballer born 1963)|Mark Wright]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}}\n|align=left|Aug 18, 2012\n|align=left|Oct 18, 2012\n|-\n|align=left|[[Stephen Azzopardi]]\n|{{flagicon|MLT}}\n|align=left|Oct 18, 2012\n|align=left|Jan 25, 2013\n|-\n|align=left|[[Iain Brunskill]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}}\n|align=left|Jan 29, 2013\n|align=left|May 8, 2013\n|-\n|align=left|[[Ian Dawes (football coach born 1984)|Ian Dawes]]\n|{{flagicon|ENG}}\n|align=left|May 9, 2013\n|align=left|April 8, 2014\n|-\n|align=left|[[Giovanni Tedesco]]\n|{{flagicon|ITA}}\n|align=left|April 8, 2014\n|align=left|May 8, 2015\n|-\n|align=left|[[Luis Oliveira]]\n|{{flagicon|BEL}}\n|align=left|June 14, 2015\n|align=left|May 8, 2016\n|-\n|align=left|[[Giovanni Tedesco]]\n|{{flagicon|ITA}}\n|align=left|June 15, 2016\n|align=left|December 4, 2017\n|-\n|-\n|align=left|Nicolas Hernan Chiesa\n|{{flagicon|ARG}}\n|align=left|December 15, 2017\n|align=left|August 27, 2018\n|-\n|align=left|[[Luis Oliveira]]\n|{{flagicon|BEL}}\n|align=left|August 28, 2018\n|align=left|November 14, 2018\n|-\n|align=left|[[Guido Ugolotti]]\n|{{flagicon|ITA}}\n|align=left|November 14, 2018\n|align=left|May 15, 2019\n|-\n|align=left|[[Vincenzo Potenza]]\n|{{flagicon|ITA}}\n|align=left|May 15, 2019<ref>{{cite news |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title= Floriana appoint Potenza as coach|url= https://www.timesofmalta.com/articles/view/20190515/football/floriana-appoint-potenza-as-coach.710053|work= Times of Malta |date= May 15, 2019|access-date= May 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|align=left|\n|-\n|}\n\n==European record==\n===Matches===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Season\n! Competition\n! Round\n! Club\n! Home\n! Away\n! Aggregate\n|-\n| [[1961\u201362 European Cup Winners' Cup|1961\u201362]]\n| [[UEFA Cup Winners' Cup|European Cup Winners' Cup